Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:56.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}狠狠地敲碎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:01:00.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}這個生鏽的世界  wow wow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:03.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}讓感情洶湧肆虐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}用力地放箭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:09.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}懷著堅定的意志  wow wow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:13.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}射穿前方的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:16.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}風聲甚至追不上我的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:19.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我的眼中只有未來
Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,Comment,,0,0,0,,——ED——
